{\"text\":\"Never gonna make you cry\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna say goodbye\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna tell a lie and hurt you\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna give you up\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna let you down\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna run around and desert you\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna make you cry\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna say goodbye\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna tell a lie and hurt you\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna give you up\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna let you down\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna run around and desert you\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna make you cry\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna say goodbye\"}","{\"text\":\"Never gonna tell a lie and hurt you\"}"],title:"一条链接",author:"某人"}));






